trans-unit.source: Contains a set of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 包含一組 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The `profile` section of the configuration file specifies a schema for user profiles.
trans-unit.target: `profile`組態檔區段會指定使用者設定檔的結構描述。

trans-unit.source: At run time, the ASP.NET compilation system uses the information specified in the `profile` section to generate a class called `ProfileCommon`, which is derived from <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileBase>.
trans-unit.target: 在執行階段，ASP.NET 編譯系統會使用指定的資訊`profile`區段，以產生類別，稱為`ProfileCommon`，其衍生自<xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileBase>。

trans-unit.source: The `ProfileCommon` class definition is based on the properties defined in the `properties` subsection of the `profile` section of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: `ProfileCommon`類別定義根據中定義的屬性`properties`小節的`profile`組態檔區段。

trans-unit.source: An instance of this class is created for each user profile, and you can access the individual profile values in your code through the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 每個使用者設定檔，建立這個類別的執行個體，您可以透過程式碼中存取個別的設定檔值<xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A>屬性。

trans-unit.source: For more information about profile properties, see [ASP.NET Profile Properties Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/89439440-92ea-48c3-a4bd-dea40307899d).
trans-unit.target: 如需有關設定檔屬性的詳細資訊，請參閱[ASP.NET 設定檔屬性概觀](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/89439440-92ea-48c3-a4bd-dea40307899d)。

trans-unit.source: For more information about the profile features added to [!INCLUDE[vstecasplong](~/includes/vstecasplong-md.md)], see [ASP.NET Profile Properties Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/89439440-92ea-48c3-a4bd-dea40307899d).
trans-unit.target: 設定檔功能的詳細資訊加入至[!INCLUDE[vstecasplong](~/includes/vstecasplong-md.md)]，請參閱[ASP.NET 設定檔屬性概觀](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/89439440-92ea-48c3-a4bd-dea40307899d)。

trans-unit.source: After checking for these conditions, the method then explicitly calls its base implementation, the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.OnDeserializeUnrecognizedElement%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.
